<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٨٨٩٣ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ قَالَ:</span> قُلْتُ لِعَطَاءٍ: بَلَغَكَ مِنْ قَوْلٍ يُسْتَحَبُّ عِنْدَ اسْتِلَامِ الرُّكْنِ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كَأَنَّهُ يَأْمُرُ بِالتَّكْبِيرِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>